code: /**  * Returns the list of input {@code StreamTransformations}.  */ public List<StreamTransformation<T>> getInputs() {     return inputs. }

@Override public Collection<StreamTransformation<?>> getTransitivePredecessors() {     List<StreamTransformation<?>> result = Lists.newArrayList().     result.add(this).     for (StreamTransformation<T> input : inputs) {         result.addAll(input.getTransitivePredecessors()).     }     return result. }
@Override public final void setChainingStrategy(ChainingStrategy strategy) {     throw new UnsupportedOperationException("Cannot set chaining strategy on Union Transformation."). }
